First the headlines were "He committed suicide while on suicide watch???"

Then it was "No he was taken off suicide watch"

Then it was "He was in solitary confinement"

Now it is "He had a cell mate who was mysteriously removed before his suicide"

When I saw the last headline on fox, I thought this was another "media reality mutation" to cover for the story on /pol/ Saturday morning that he was seen being removed (cover being it was cellmate seen removed):
>>fb3684ad-10be-4e70-a255-b245f5f2b142

But then it says the cellmate was removed Friday so nope.

Sure looks like a lot of scrambling for narrative control...

https://iotwreport.com/former-head-of-nyc-prisons-if-epstein-was-in-solitary-confinement-he-wasnt-on-suicide-watch/

https://www.foxnews.com/us/jeffrey-epstein-checked-for-hours-apparent-suicide

Ok guys are we done?  Defeated that easily?

They took over halfchan long ago and deleted/banned everything 8ch refugees have tried to do.

They've hit us hard here on zero with shilling, division, [cp|hate|terrorist|violence] traps, and scared most away.

They've shutdown endchan.

#qanon is dead on twitter with mostly paid shills being all I'm seeing.


So we just give up?  This entire movement has been about waking up the people, and re-teaching us how to fight, and suddenly when Q can't talk to us and prop us up, we go right back to helpless sheep with no fight in us.

Dust off the memes about censorship.  Re-activate the political strategy war rooms.  Fight what they've done to 8ch and others, and call out their lies & projection & fake posting designed to make us look like violent crazy people.  Do it with class, logic, and data - NOT with violence.

Q would say FIGHT FIGHT FIGHT!
But not with violence of course, with MEME's of truth!

Light twitter back up and drive home our points harder than ever!

So what the fuck happened to zero?

Main site now doesn't even show the QResearch board now.

Searching for qr shows the fake QResearch 2nd board named Noob dig - NOT the one with the old breads.  

Searching for the address 17rEeDwJ1UrHPHSrqspzTQJVPAFFxK8xtS finds nothing!

But if you keep clicking the Load More button under Recent posts, you'll find dedicated anons posting the latest QResearch posts and can click it to get here.

Sure feels like everything is comped now.  If there's another bunker besides this & endchan, please share with lost anons and cross post.

Q may be blacked out for a while, but we need a place for the research to continue and the hive mind to function instead of just dangling.

God bless POTUS, Q, Anons!

If you have VLC installed, you can use it to save videos directly to your computer.  It's extra steps, but it saves the real, unadulterated file locally instead of an archive site that can be wiped later too.

Just enter the youtube address in the open network stream dialog of VLC, and then when it opens, right click in the video and select tools -> codec information (or shortcut ctrl-j).  When the codec window opens, there's a location box at the bottom.  Copy/paste everything in that location box into a browser address, and it will start playing the video directly in the browser.  Then right click the video in the browser window, and you can save video as ...
Easily save .mp4 directly to hd that way.
